    • Constructor Detail

      • ReadCSV

        public ReadCSV(java.lang.String filename)
        Reads a CSV-formatted text file. Column names (first line of CSV file) are stored in their of ArrayList<String>. Each line is splitted according to the DELIM delimiter and the result is stored in an ArrayList<String>. All lines are stored in an ArrayList<ArrayList<String>>.
        Parameters:
        filename - the CSV file name to parse
